"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"human_soldier_operative\"]/short"
msgstr "Soldier"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:61
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"human_soldier_operative\"]/powerList/power[1]"
msgstr "Inflicts 1.2x damage in combat"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:62
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"human_soldier_operative\"]/powerList/power[2]"
msgstr "Takes 0.7x damage from combat and 0.6x from fires"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:63
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"human_soldier_operative\"]/powerList/power[3]"
msgstr "Learns skills much faster"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:68
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Uptors are Alpha Gouls stabilized in special RadiKal Scorch pressure cookers, changing their properties.\n"
"\t\tYour system in the current room is immune to fire. Any enemy system in the current room takes 100% more fire damage.\n"
"\t\tCan cause yoctoflares from its own body often. That's a very small solar flare, but it's also very close.\n"
"\n"
"\tInherited phantom stats: takes no damage from hazards, has door phasing properties."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:74
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/title"
msgstr "Uptor"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:75
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/short"
msgstr "Uptor"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:78
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/powerList/power[1]"
msgstr ""
"Active Ability: Start a fire in a random room on both ships. Short cooldown"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:79
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/powerList/power[2]"
msgstr "Max Health is increased to 220"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:80
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/powerList/power[3]"
msgstr "Can't split, repair or extinguish. No sabotage bonus"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:81
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/powerList/power[4]"
msgstr "Movement speed is increased to 1.2x"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:82
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//crewBlueprint[@name=\"rk_fireghost\"]/powerList/power[5]"
msgstr "Inflicts 1.5x damage in crew combat"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:107
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/title"
msgstr "Shipvore Ram"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:108
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The signature combat augment of the RadiKal Bam lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, full power uses more and destroys the augment. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]\n"
"\tCan be reinforced at empty beacons to survive the next Full Power use."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:117
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"LOCKED_DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/title"
msgstr "Shipvore Ram"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:118
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"LOCKED_DJMOD_COMBAT_SHIPVORE_RAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The signature combat augment of the RadiKal Bam lets you repeatedly ram the enemy for guaranteed quickly lethal damage, free repairs and sometimes other things. WARNING: your ship and/or crew may suffer. [Uses {, full power uses more. Emergency Generator and Fuel Conserver can apply.]\n"
"\t\n"
"\tThe ship was built around this locked version that survives Full Power use. Also gives 9% faster shield recharge and chance to ignore hull damage."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:129
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_OFF\"]/title"
msgstr "Charged Belts (Off)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:130
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_OFF\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This augment is Off but can be toggled On anytime. When On: \n"
"\t[This double-edged augment from the RadiKal Bam equips your crew with belts that reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Ghosts) and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms.\n"
"\tStacks upon already existing death effects.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCannot be toggled Off but can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.\n"
"\n"
"\tCOMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter.]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:143
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_ON\"]/title"
msgstr "Charged Belts"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:144
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_CREW_ARE_BOMBS_ON\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This double-edged augment from the RadiKal Bam equips your crew with belts that reduce their HP by 10% (beware of Ghosts) and explode when they die, causing a fire and dealing damage to the room and ship they're in, with extra damage in systemless rooms.\n"
"\tStacks upon already existing death effects.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCannot be toggled Off but can scrap itself into ~ or } at empty beacons.\n"
"\n"
"\tCOMBO: Makes any crew a fire source for Plasma Teleporter."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:157
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_AUG_AUTO_SYS_REPAIR\"]/title"
msgstr "A.E.R.A. Second Wind"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:158
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_AUG_AUTO_SYS_REPAIR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"'Automated Emergency Repair Augment', by RadiKal Bam engineers. When active,"
" if your ship is almost destroyed (5 hull or less), a nanomachine burst will"
" be released in your systems, fully repairing them as well as 8 hull points,"
" and destroying the augment. No effect if your hull instantly reaches 0. "
"[Activation uses 1 power]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:195
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_EXTRACTOR\"]/title"
msgstr "RK Shield (1)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:196
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ZOLTAN_SHIELD_EXTRACTOR\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Punk augment provides 1 layer of supershields, for when you "
"really just want to avoid immediate mind control, teleport or hacking "
"issues."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:204
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_OFFENSE_DISABLER\"]/title"
msgstr "Offense Disabler"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:205
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_OFFENSE_DISABLER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Punk combat augment disables enemy offensive systems (Weapons, Drone Control, Hacking, Mind Control, Teleporter, and one Artillery) for 5 seconds. The effect then weakens progressively until it's gone at 18 seconds (you will be warned).\n"
"\t\tPerfect against aggressive enemies! [Uses 3| and 3 reactor power. Emergency Generator can apply.]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:227
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_HACK_FLEET\"]/title"
msgstr "Enigmashin"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:228
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_HACK_FLEET\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Punk combat augment needs a level 2 Hacking system on your ship. \n"
"\tAttempts to send deepfake intel to the rebels through an enemy's comms for credibility.\n"
"\tOn average, success delays the fleet 75% of the time and failure accelerates it 10% of the time. If you deal more than 2 hull damage during the process, it stops. [Reduces player Hacking power by 2 for 17s, uses 2|]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:237
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_SUPER_DEFENDERS\"]/title"
msgstr "Defense Kits"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:238
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_SUPER_DEFENDERS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Punk augment makes your crew better at survival on your ship.\n"
"\tx0.75 damage taken, x1.3 repair speed, x1.3 movement speed, and a 4 HP/second heal while idle (not even manning)."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:247
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_OWN_HARMONY_ON\"]/title"
msgstr "Punk Harmony"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:248
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_OWN_HARMONY_ON\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Some daft RadiKal Punks made their own Harmony. Controls your Engis on your ship, giving them immunity to (further) mind control and +40% damage and stun resistance. Powered levels in Hacking or Mind Control add 5/10/20/40/80/160% combat damage, and repair and movement speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tIn short, makes them harder, better, faster, stronger, and automated.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be toggled off anytime."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:258
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_OWN_HARMONY_OFF\"]/title"
msgstr "Punk Harmony (OFF)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:259
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_OWN_HARMONY_OFF\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Some daft RadiKal Punks made their own Harmony. Controls your Engis on your ship, giving them immunity to (further) mind control and +40% damage and stun resistance. Powered levels in Hacking or Mind Control add 5/10/20/40/80/160% combat damage, and repair and movement speed.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tIn short, makes them harder, better, faster, stronger, and automated.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be toggled on anytime."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:270
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_DEFENSE_REMOVER\"]/title"
msgstr "Vulnerabilizer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:271
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_DEFENSE_REMOVER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This powerful RadiKal Punk combat augment slowly weakens the enemy's "
"defenses. Every 3 to 7 seconds (at random), limits enemy Shields and Engines"
" by 1 power. This effect stacks. All effects end after a duration based on "
"how many | you spent.[Uses 3 reactor power. Emergency Generator can apply.]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:287
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF\"]/title"
msgstr "Scorched Earth (T1)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:288
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"On both ships, this RadiKal Scorch augment makes your crew take 40% less fire damage and get x3 extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second +2 per powered level in O2.\n"
"\tActivate from the Toggles menu to set specific systems on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCOMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be upgraded twice at empty beacons."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:301
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF_2\"]/title"
msgstr "Blazing Earth (T2)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:302
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF_2\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[Tier 2 Scorched Earth] On both ships, this RadiKal Scorch augment makes your crew take 55% less fire damage and get x3 extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second +2 per powered level in O2.\n"
"\tIn fire, they move and sabotage at x2 speed and deal x2 damage.\n"
"\tActivate from the Toggles menu to set specific systems on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCOMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be upgraded once at empty beacons."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:317
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF_3\"]/title"
msgstr "Erupting Earth (T3)"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:318
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_SELF_3\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"[Tier 3 Scorched Earth] On both ships, this RadiKal Scorch augment makes your crew take 70% less fire damage and get x3 extinguishing. While extinguishing, they also heal 2 HP/second +2 per powered level in O2.\n"
"\tIn fire, they move and sabotage at x2 speed, deal x2 damage, and produce O2 like 2 Orchids.\n"
"\tAlso, enemy crew and drones in fire lose 7 hp per second.\n"
"\tActivate from the Toggles menu to set specific systems on your ship (or the whole ship) on fire to fight boarders.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCOMBO: Plasma Teleporter moves the augment's fire to the enemy ship."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:344
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_ENEMY\"]/title"
msgstr "Plasma Teleporter"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:345
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_COMBAT_SCORCH_ENEMY\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This combat augment from the RadiKal Scorch can set the enemy ship on fire at start of combat, outright winning some fights.\n"
"\t\tNeeds a fire source: RK firestarting equipment, Gouls, Lost Suns, Shells, Zoltans, or 3}.\n"
"\t\t[Uses 1{, ignites your O2 system.]\n"
"\n"
"\tCOMBO: Charged Belts / Martyr Vests make all crew fire sources.\n"
"\tCOMBO: any Scorched Earth can provide the fire for free."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:357
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ENEMIES_CAN_BURN\"]/title"
msgstr "Flammabilizer-Immune"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:358
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ENEMIES_CAN_BURN\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Scorch augment removes the fire immunity and resistance of enemies by limiting their total fire resistance, based on the energy in your O2 system (90/75/55/30 resistance at 0/1/2/3 power respectively).\n"
"\tAlso makes enemies move 12% slower in fire (up to 50% with 3 power in O2).\n"
"\tWorks on both ships.\n"
"\n"
"\tCan be toggled to make non-fireproof enemies take more fire damage instead."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:368
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ENEMIES_BURN_MORE\"]/title"
msgstr "Flammabilizer-Damage"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:369
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ENEMIES_BURN_MORE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Scorch augment makes non-fireproof enemies take 50% more fire damage (scaling up to 250% with 4 energy in O2).\n"
"\tAlso makes enemies move 12% slower in fire (up to 50% with 3 power in O2).\n"
"\tWorks on both ships.\n"
"\t\n"
"\tCan be toggled to make fireproof and fire-resistant enemies vulnerable to fire instead."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:380
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_OXYGENIZER\"]/title"
msgstr "Oxygenizer"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:381
msgid "data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_OXYGENIZER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Scorch combat augment can basically shoot out giant canisters of ultracompressed O2 to fill the void of space when a fight starts.\n"
"\tPuts both ship in an atmosphere, making breaches and open vents fill oxygen instead of depleting it. Shenanigans ensue. [Uses 2}]"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:479
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_MC_IMMUNE_FROM_FIRE\"]/title"
msgstr "Mind Heater"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:480
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_MC_IMMUNE_FROM_FIRE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"In fire, your crew are immune to Mind Control and stunned 50% shorter. Works"
" on both ships."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:487
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/title"
msgstr "Demicloners"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:488
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"INTERNAL_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The RadiKal Punk infused these backpack-clonebay prototypes with dark energies. These try to resurrect your crew if they die (not in events) when you don't have a real Clonebay.\n"
"\t\tAt best, crew resurrect as their own lesser version (Soldier = default Human, etc.) If no lesser version exists, they become Morphs. When Morphs die, nothing happens."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:497
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/title"
msgstr "[X] Demicloners"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:498
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//augBlueprint[@name=\"EX_DJMOD_DEMICLONER\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"The RadiKal Punk infused these backpack-clonebay prototypes with dark energies. These try to resurrect your crew if they die (not in events) when you don't have a real Clonebay.\n"
"\t\tAt best, crew resurrect as their own lesser version (Soldier = default Human, etc.) If no lesser version exists, they become Morphs. When Morphs die, nothing happens.\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t[X] - As an external system upgrade, this augment will provide its normal effect but take up an augment slot. Can be converted for free to the internal version under the internal upgrade menu."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:632
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/title"
msgstr "'Bada' Fissure Beam"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:633
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/short"
msgstr "'Bada Beam'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:634
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_BAM_FISSUREBEAM\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Fissure Beams deal damage per tile rather than per room. This RadiKal Bam beam can only hit about 4, but hard. Has hullbust.\n"
"\t\tBest at destroying a large system in one sweep, or a ship by targeting systemless room tiles."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:768
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/title"
msgstr "Rain of Ions"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:769
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/short"
msgstr "RainIons"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:772
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_ION\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Punk inaccurate shotgun fires an accelerated phase ion, a heavy ion, a fire ion, a normal ion, a stun ion, and a radion (from fastest to slowest) all at once. Chains cooldown up to 8 times.\n"
"\t\tMany weapons worth of blue options!"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:850
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE\"]/title"
msgstr "Rain of fire"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:851
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE\"]/short"
msgstr "RainFire"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:852
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"This RadiKal Scorch weapon does one thing: sustain fires even in fireproof "
"ships, with a rain of napalm. No damage but pierces all shields. 80% chance "
"to not use a missile. Great with dedicated fire augments."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:906
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE_ENEMYFIX\"]/title"
msgstr "Rain of fire"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:907
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE_ENEMYFIX\"]/short"
msgstr "RainFire"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:908
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_RAIN_OF_FIRE_ENEMYFIX\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"YOU SHOULD NEVER SEE THIS. Shots limited to 3 and cooldown reduced to avoid "
"game freeze when: (shots > player ship rooms) due to the way AI targets."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:953
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_LASER_BPS\"]/title"
msgstr "'BPS Messenger'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:954
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_LASER_BPS\"]/short"
msgstr "'BPS Mess.'"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:956
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_LASER_BPS\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"A Piercing Heavy Laser boosted in the RadiKal sector: the Bam gave it "
"hullbust and better stun, the Punk added ion and crew damage, and the Scorch"
" replaced breach chance with guaranteed fire and chaining."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1020
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ARTILLERY_MISSILE_FIRE\"]/title"
msgstr "Fire Missile Artillery"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1021
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ARTILLERY_MISSILE_FIRE\"]/short"
msgstr "Artillery"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1022
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ARTILLERY_MISSILE_FIRE\"]/desc"
msgstr ""
"Artillery: Fires 3 missiles that do 1 hull damage each, always start a fire and never miss.\n"
"\tBase Cooldown: 18"

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1024
msgid ""
"data/blueprints.xml.append$//weaponBlueprint[@name=\"DJMOD_ARTILLERY_MISSILE_FIRE\"]/tooltip"
msgstr ""
"Artillery: Fires 3 missiles that do 1 hull damage each, always start a fire "
"and never miss."

#: src-en/data/blueprints.xml.append:1063
